List principal owner citations

list_principal_owner_citations.Rd

List principal owner citations

list_principal_owner_citations(principalOwner, env = "production")

Arguments

principalOwner

(character) Principal owner in the format returned by construct_dn()
env

(character) Repository environment. Can be: "production", "staging", or "development".

Value

(xml_document) Journal citations metadata for all entries owned by the specified principal owner

See also

Other Journal Citations: create_journal_citation(), delete_journal_citation(), get_journal_citation(), list_data_package_citations()

Examples

# List citations
dn <- create_dn(userId = "FCE", ou = "EDI")

#> Error in create_dn(userId = "FCE", ou = "EDI"): could not find function "create_dn"
journalCitations <- list_principal_owner_citations(principalOwner = dn)

#> Error in list_principal_owner_citations(principalOwner = dn): could not find function "list_principal_owner_citations"
journalCitations

#> Error in eval(expr, envir, enclos): object 'journalCitations' not found
